      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "UNDER ANESTHETIC (1) recorded a win over the 515m at The Gardens in a good 29.74 last start. Hot win latest and looks the one to beat again. IT'S A GLAM (2) finished second (30.07) two back at The Gardens but out of the placings last time when 6th there. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from six attempts. Has ability and can measure up. OXLEY DREAM GIRL (3) goes very well at the course and distance with three wins and a placing from eight starts. Comes off a (30.63) win last time, scoring by 2.5 lengths in a Grade 5 over 525m at this track. Can hit the frame with the right run. MAJOR FLIRT (8) will give backers a sight.",
